Given an Image returns a vector with the local maxima and local minima of the given image.

Parameters
[in]pimgPointer to the image
[out]local_minimaReturn the points of the local minima contour
[out]local_maximaReturn the points of the local maxima contour
[in]threshold_whiteMore than this value is considered black
[in]threshold_blackLess than this value is set to white
[in]local_contextThe number of pixels in stroke that is used to compute the local maxima/minima
[in]duplicate_intervalThe minimum distance of locals within the same stroke

return result_Point2D;

return result_Point2D;
